/a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#编译装载结果\">编译装载结果</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /TOC -->\n<h2 id=\"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\"><a href=\"#linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\"></a><code>linux</code>字符设备驱动设计与实现</h2><h3 id=\"TDLCD-Test-Device-For-Linux-Char-Drives-的设计\"><a href=\"#TDLCD-Test-Device-For-Linux-Char-Drives-的设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)的设计\"></a><code>TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)</code>的设计</h3><ul>\n<li><p>主要参考<code>Linux Device Drives</code>第三章-字符设备驱动程序中的<code>scull(Simple Chararter Utility for Loading Localities)</code></p>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/15/FEtM5AmhCq1Nl8y.jpg","content":null,"text":"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)的设计TDLCD实现步骤结构设计模块部分宏定义及头文件字符设备结构设计file_operations结构设计字符设备模块的加载与卸载函数Makefile编译装载结果li","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":6,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"},{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":7,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"}]},{"title":"copy-virtual-ubuntu","slug":"copy-virtual-ubuntu","date":"2019-11-13T10:47:21.000Z","updated":"2019-12-06T03:22:09.129Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/copy-virtual-ubuntu.json","excerpt":"<!-- TOC -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\">解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡<code>eth0</code></a><ul>\n<li><a href=\"#背景\">背景</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#原因\">原因</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#解决办法\">解决办法</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#参考链接\">参考链接</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /TOC -->\n<h1 id=\"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\"><a href=\"#解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\"></a>解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡<code>eth0</code></h1><h2 id=\"背景\"><a href=\"#背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"背景\"></a>背景</h2><p>最近在学习Linux程序设计及驱动相关知识，买了宝华老师的书，但是在把baohua_linux复制到本地之后，从虚拟机进入ifconfig，只有lo网络，没有其他网卡，虚拟机的网络适配器设置为NAT模式。<br>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0背景原因解决办法参考链接解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0背景最近在学习Linux程序设计及驱动相关知识，买了宝华老师的书，但是在把baohua_linux复制到本地之后，从虚拟机进入ifconfig，只有lo网络，没有其他网卡，虚拟机的网络","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":7,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"vmware","slug":"vmware","count":1,"path":"api/tags/vmware.json"},{"name":"network","slug":"network","count":1,"path":"api/tags/network.json"}]},{"title":"build-hello-module-in-linux","slug":"build-hello-module-in-linux","date":"2019-11-13T02:49:12.000Z","updated":"2019-11-18T11:25:20.685Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/build-hello-module-in-linux.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"编译简单的linux内核模块\"><a href=\"#编译简单的linux内核模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译简单的linux内核模块\"></a>编译简单的<code>linux</code>内核模块</h1>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/1zoMHxPZeOBiFSr.jpg","content":null,"text":"编译简单的linux内核模块hello.c1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>11<br>12<br>13<br>14<br>15<br>16<br>17<br>18<br>19<br>20<br>21<br>22","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":7,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"module","slug":"module","count":1,"path":"api/tags/module.json"}]},{"title":"config-kernel-arm","slug":"config-kernel-arm","date":"2019-11-13T02:34:34.000Z","updated":"2019-11-20T13:38:47.955Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/config-kernel-arm.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"linux-内核的配置\"><a href=\"#linux-内核的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux 内核的配置\"></a><code>linux</code> 内核的配置</h1>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":null,"text":"linux 内核的配置四种打开方式make configmake menuconfigmake xconfigmake gconfigmenuconfig 如下所示 [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":6,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"},{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":7,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"}]}]}